### Input: GeoJSON object
```
{&quot;features&quot;:[{&quot;geometry&quot;:{&quot;coordinates&quot;:[[[76.767318,33.228753],[76.767318,33.228753]]],&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Polygon&quot;},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Feature&quot;,&quot;properties&quot;:{&quot;State_Code&quot;:&quot;01&quot;,&quot;State_Name&quot;:&quot;ABC&quot;}},{&quot;geometry&quot;:{&quot;coordinates&quot;:[[[79.008814,31.115041],[79.008814,31.115041]]],&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Polygon&quot;},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Feature&quot;,&quot;properties&quot;:{&quot;State_Code&quot;:&quot;02&quot;,&quot;State_Name&quot;:&quot;DEF&quot;}},{&quot;geometry&quot;:{&quot;coordinates&quot;:[[[76.942524,30.383268],[76.850815,30.717589],[76.852673,30.718222],[76.853471,30.718813]]],&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Polygon&quot;},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Feature&quot;,&quot;properties&quot;:{&quot;State_Code&quot;:&quot;03&quot;,&quot;State_Name&quot;:&quot;GHI&quot;}}],&quot;crs&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;name&quot;,&quot;properties&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84&quot;}},&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Some Boundary&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;FeatureCollection&quot;}
```

### Output: List of Postgis POLYGON geometry (as TEXT)
```
